  A Second-Level Domain (SLD).
  It matches all Top-Level Domains (TLD), and subdomains that include the Domain.
  Example: example.com.
  """
  domain: [Domain!]!
  "An exact match of the fully qualified domain (FQDN). Example: www.my.example.com."
